  {name: "Cline Collection ", category: "dining", description: "With subtle country aesthetic lending distinct influence to the design of the Cline Collection it will place perfectly in your traditional casual dining space. Gently curved arms descend from the traditional Windsor back chair creating an inviting environment in which to enjoy your meal or conversation time. The rectangular table top features rounded corners that enhance the updated style. The two tone finish lends visual contrast making this a unique choice for your dining space.", image: "https://www.homelegance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/5530-78__1-750x500.jpg"},
