  {name: "Mattawa Collection ", category: "dining", description: "Rustic industrial styling heavily influences the design of the Mattawa Collection. Metal banded rivet accenting provides visual contrast to the chairs, table and server of this casual dining collection. The brown finish has hints of gray undertone lending to the rustic look. Accompanying the collection is the server, featuring drawers and behind door storage.", image: "https://www.homelegance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/5518-78__1-750x500.jpg"},
