  {name: "Orpheus Collection ", category: "dining", description: "In keeping with the spirit of the need for versatility within the more modest of dining spaces, the Orpheus Collection provides function and style making it the perfect addition to your home. Mid-century modern design is immediately discernable as you take in the collectionâ\u0080\u0099s profile. Stacking chairs allow for quick and compact storage, while the natural pine finish of the legs and gray finish of the table top, chair backs and seats lend to the contemporary styling.", image: "https://www.homelegance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/5515GY__1-750x500.jpg"},
