  {name: "Seaford Collection ", category: "dining", description: "Subtle industrial influence creates the visual appeal of the casual dining tables of the Seaford Collection. V-matched veneer is finished in a gray tone highlights the tone variation of the wood grain. Angled trestle bases support the table tops of the collection while X-back chairs feature bi-cast vinyl padded seats for comfort.", image: "https://www.homelegance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/5510-66__1-750x500.jpg"},
