  {name: "Savion Collection ", category: "dining", description: "Sophisticated soft contemporary design is achieved in your dining room with the addition of the Savion Collection. Two table types are offered as versatile options to fit in your space â\u0080\u0093 a rectangular double pedestal table and an oval single pedestal table. Both featuring a distinct birdcage style base. An espresso finish highlights the unique veneer pattern. Dramatic flair is lent to the design by the accompanying chairs. Neutral tone fabric covers the substantially sized roll back arm and side chairs. Reeded fronts on the server along with the serpentine profile further the elegance of this distinctly sophisticated collection.", image: "https://www.homelegance.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/5494-106__1-750x500.jpg"},
