  {name: "Kase Collection ", category: "bedroom", description: "Covered in a neutral tone brown fabric, nail head accent and featuring a gently curved headboard, the Kase Collection will be the perfect addition to your modern traditional bedroom.", image: "https://www.homelegance.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/1888N-1HB__1-750x500.jpg"},
