  {name: "4690-F3 4690-F4 Recife Collection ", category: "seating", description: "From the boudoir to the parlor, the Recife Collection adds a touch of glamour anywhere it goes. This fully upholstered accent ottoman is offered in the chic hues of indigo, beige, and dark grey â\u0080\u0093 all featuring nail head accent that trims the profile of the seat base and X-leg supports.", image: "https://www.homelegance.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/4690-F__1__4690-F2_____4690-F3_4690-F41-750x500.jpg"},
  {name: "Madoc Collection ", category: "seating", description: "Transforming before your eyes is the Madoc Collection. Starting with plush seating and back for your comfort, armrests open to reveal storage space while the center headrest of the sofa rises to illuminate the drop down back of the center seat, cup holders further the use of this table-like platform. Contoured for your comfort and covered in black leather gel match, the multi-functional contemporary design is furthered by touch button reclining and power headrest adjustment.", image: "https://www.homelegance.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/8444BLK-3PW__1-750x500.jpg"},
