  {name: "Center Hill Collection ", category: "seating", description: "With plush seating that is uncommon in most traditional looks, the design of Center Hill Collection will be a welcome addition to your living room. Offered in bonded leather match, the covering comes in either dark brown or black. With traditional nailhead accent lending an elegant statement to each piece and the easy recline mechanisms adding to the comfort, the lovely Center Hill Collection will provide your friends and family a warm environment to spend their quality moment. The collection is also available in power reclining mechanism.", image: "https://www.homelegance.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/9668BRW-3PW__1-750x500.jpg"},
  {name: "Talon Collection ", category: "seating", description: "Designed with numerous room decors in mind, the transitional Talon Collection will be the perfect option for your living room. This stationary group features amply stuffed seating and a bonded leather match covering that is offered in either taupe or black.", image: "https://www.homelegance.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/8511BK__1-750x500.jpg"},
